race.comment: MAGIC WYLDE (4) has mixed form recently, finishing seventh (22.41) in a NG at Gosford latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Will find this more suitable and can atone. GARIN (1) finds it hard to win but looks close to breaking through. Has hit the frame the last two runs, the latest when third (23.63) at this track. Well placed and gets his chance. SOLO FERNANDO (7) has been hard to follow lately, running seventh (23.02) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at Maitland. Can feature with the right run. GOLD RUSH LAD (8) racing over this course and distance brings the best out in him.
